name: International 14 Series Axial Flow
description:
This is my heavy edit of Matt26's International 14 Axial Flow combine. I take no credit for his work and I just wanted to do this and release it myself

Changes include :

Removing and changing the base model for things that werent on the real 14, added different sounds, changed the skinny rear 2wd wheels, edited the xml a little bit, changed the 1030 to an 820 header (close enough) and much more

I have started a scratch built 14 combine but I dont have the motivation to finish the whole thing as it is a lot of work but I think this edit will do for now

Ive also included Hamberglers converted 963 and 983 corn heads ready to fit on the 14

Thank you to all of my close friends for keeping in touch with me and being, friends. I love you all.
